import Navbar from './components/Navbar';
import './App.css';


function App() {
  let Component 
  switch (window.location.pathname){
    case "/" :
      Component = App
      break
      case "/one":
        Component = One
        break
        case "/two":
          Component = Two
          break
          case "/three":
            Component = Three
            break
  }
  return (<>
  <Navbar/>
  <Component/>
  </>)
}

export default App;
